<plot>In a small village by the sea on the coast of Lazio (Italy) twelve year old Adriana spends the summer with her sister Francesca. Involved by her sister in a strange game, the little girl starts an ambiguous relationship with a boy younger than her, Tommaso, who's the image of the innocence that Adriana is about to lose.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?350093</url></doc>
